{{Quote|When Targaryen fought Targaryen in the civil war called the Dance of the Dragons, an angry mob stormed the Dragonpit, that huge now-ruined vault where Targaryens stabled their beasts. Thousands died, but through sheer numbers and madness, five of the Targaryen dragons lay dead by the morning.|[[Pycelle]]|Dragons (Histories &amp; Lore)}}
The '''Dragonpit''' is a huge vault located in [[King's Landing]]. [[House Targaryen]] used it to stable their [[dragons]].
